<div class = "row large-12 columns">
    <h4> How can we help? </h4>
    <ul class='circles'>
      <li><b>Technical Assistance</b> – national civil society alliances can apply for technical assistance from the SUN CSN secretariat. Technical assistance can cover a range of areas including Governance, Fundraising, Advocacy and Communications. To apply for technical assistance please fill in our application form <%= link_to 'here', 'https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc24FQcJH7RYtBSKrK67iewgrPY6SirnVTJYFER-3urvm1Sfg/viewform', class:"blink" %>.</li>
      <li><b>Communications</b> – the SUN CSN works closely with the wider nutrition and development community, maintaining oversight of the latest plans and opportunities  linked to nutrition. We can help to connect you to others working on similar issues or in your geographic location or signpost you to relevant opportunities. We also publish quarterly newsletters with updates from the network  – subscribe here.</li>
      <li><b>Events</b> – the SUN CSN organised a range of events linked to learning exchange and advocacy. You can find a calendar of upcoming events <%= link_to 'here', 'https://calendar.google.com/calendar/render?pli=1#main_7', class:"blink" %>.</li>
      <li><b>Resources</b> - The SUN CSN secretariat develops guidance and resources to support civil society to scale up nutrition. You can find all our resources in our resource library <%= link_to 'here', knowledge_path, class:"blink" %>.
  </div>
